msgstr "replace-block kræver et \"block\"-objekt med et \"name\"-felt."

#: includes/class-block-mutator.php:341
#, php-format
msgid "Removing synced pattern reference \"%s\". The pattern itself is not deleted."
msgstr "Fjerner synkroniseret mønsterreference \"%s\". Mønstret selv slettes ikke."

